rde@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-lorde@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-lorde@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩</a>透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">洛德</a>向她发送了一系列应对消极情绪和她迅速成名的方法——请在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">Chappell Roan：流行超新星，感觉就像“变装皇后”女孩之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月，罗恩在 TikTok 上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-chastises-fans-weird-and-creepy-behaviour-thats-not-normal-3785060">分享了她对出名的看法以及随之而来的“奇怪”和“令人毛骨悚然”的粉丝行为</a>。她质疑是否允许有人在车里对她大喊大叫，因为她拒绝拍照而生她的气，跟踪她，或者仅仅因为她是名人而不是“随机的女人”而骚扰她。 “我是一个随意的婊子。你就是个随意的贱人。想一想，”她在第一次 TikTok 中说道。</p><p>在另一段视频中，她说，仅仅因为骚扰“对名人或小名气的人来说是很正常的事情”，“这并不意味着它就可以”或“正常”，也不是她希望对她做的事情。 </p><figure id="attachment_3792894" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792894" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792894" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan-vmas@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3792894" class="wp-caption-text">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 出席 2024 年 MTV VMA 颁奖典礼。图片来源：Mike Coppola/Getty Images for MTV</figcaption></figure><p>在她对粉丝行为发表评论后，众多音乐界大腕向这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">前<em>NME 封面</em>明星</a>伸出援手，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/katy-perry">Katy Perry</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muna">MUNA</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">Miley Cyrus</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">boygenius</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mitski">Mitski</a> 。</p><p>洛德也向她伸出了援手——尽管查普尔·罗恩现在透露，这位新西兰人不仅只是鼓励的话，还与她分享了如何应对这种情况的八个建议。</p><p>罗恩在接受<a href="https://theface.com/music/chappell-roan-pop-music-famous-interview-good-luck-babe" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《The Face》</em></a>采访时表示：“我觉得名声就是一种侮辱。这种氛围——跟踪、在网上说废话、[那些人]不肯让你孤单、在公共场合对你大喊大叫——就是一个虐待前夫的氛围。就是这样的感觉。我不知道这种感觉会这么糟糕。” </p><figure id="attachment_3774359" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3774359" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3774359" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Lorde-performing-live-CREDIT-Photo-by-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="洛德现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Lorde-performing-live-CREDIT-Photo-by-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Lorde-performing-live-CREDIT-Photo-by-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Lorde-performing-live-CREDIT-Photo-by-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Lorde-performing-live-CREDIT-Photo-by-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Lorde-performing-live-CREDIT-Photo-by-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Lorde-performing-live-CREDIT-Photo-by-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3774359" class="wp-caption-text">洛德现场表演 – 图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImag/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>有一天，她在机场的浴室里哭泣，给洛德发短信寻求建议：“她给我发了一份我应该做的事情清单。从字面上写下八件事，她希望有人在她经历这件事时告诉她。她经历了该死的地狱。她还是个婴儿！”</p><p>在罗恩向粉丝发布视频之前，她曾表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-shes-pumped-the-brakes-on-fame-after-fans-give-off-stalker-vibes-3775922">，在粉丝发出“跟踪狂的感觉”后，她想“踩刹车”</a> 。她的言论赢得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Paramore">Paramore</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/aritsts/Hayley-Williams">Hayley Williams</a>的赞扬，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramores-hayley-williams-supports-chappell-roans-brave-and-unfortunately-necessary-boundary-comments-3787404">在 Instagram 上称赞这位流行歌星“勇敢”</a> 。</p><p>上周在 MTV VMA 的其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-snaps-back-at-vmas-photographer-who-seemingly-told-her-to-shut-the-fuck-up-3792891">罗恩回击了一位摄影师，后者似乎告诉她在红地毯上“他妈的闭嘴”</a> 。在颁奖典礼之前，这位冉冉升起的流行歌星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappel-roan-cancels-number-of-european-shows-due-to-scheduling-conflicts-3788740">因“日程安排冲突”而取消了两场欧洲演出，</a>遭到了一些强烈反对。随后她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-fans-react-after-she-posts-vma-rehearsal-photos-ahead-of-cancelled-gigs-3790886">发布了自己在 VMA 排练中的照片</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3792987" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792987" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792987" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ChappellRoan-MTV-VMAs-debut-performance.jpg" alt="Chappell Roan 在 2024 年 MTV VMA 舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https